---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { useTranslations } from "../../i18n/ui";

const t = useTranslations("en");
---

<BaseLayout lang="en" title={t("about")}>
  <section class="page-head">
    <h1>{t("about")}</h1>
    <p>{t("aboutIntro")}</p>
  </section>

  <section class="home-hero">
    <div class="home-copy-wrap">
      <div class="home-copy">
        <p>
          Although Marx spends most of the time asleep, he reads a great many books and newspaper whenever he is awake. He has a fondness for opera, theatre, and contemporary art. You’re likely to find him in a museum or an opera house. If you spend enough time wandering the internet, you might also happen to stumble across him somewhere in its deeper recesses. Marx has a particular interest in folk culture, horror films, and interactive games.
        </p>

        <p>
          He is deeply interested in observing the material world and exploring the inner terrain of the human mind. Although his educational background includes business, law, and Buddhist studies, Marx is ultimately most drawn to those subtle subjects that resist easy articulation.
        </p>

        <p>
          “Marx” is a variant of “Marcus”, derived from “Mars”, the Roman god of war. It carries no particular political meaning. If one absolutely had to assign him a political stance, it would be: Fully Automated Luxury LGBTQIA+ Space Communism.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="home-media">
      <div class="image-frame">
        <img src="/images/About.jpg" alt="About image" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .home-head {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .home-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(320px, 440px);
      align-items: start;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .home-copy-wrap {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .home-copy {
      max-width: 460px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }


    .home-media {
      width: 100%;
      justify-self: end;
    }

    .image-frame {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 440px;
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
      border-radius: 28px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    }

    .image-frame img {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    @media (max-width: 840px) {
      .home-hero {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 28px;
      }

      .home-media {
        order: -1;
        justify-self: start;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .image-frame {
        max-width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
      }

      .home-copy {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
